description: Perfection! Amazing 2100SF home ALL ON ONE LEVEL! Boutique Elevator Building built in 2017! 3 Bedrooms & 2 Designer bathrooms! 2 Garage Parking Spaces!(Huge roof deck with jaw-dropping vistas & 2 additional private decks! Impressive Open Living room, Dining room, & Chef's gourmet Kitchen all framed with Oversized Windows! Striking top-of-the-line appliances including Sub Zero refrigerator & Wolf commercial grade 6-burner stainless steel stove! Immense 10 foot center island! Abundant European cabinetry, endless Quartz countertops, easy-access pantry & wet bar for memorable cooking & entertaining! Deck off Living Room with gas line for year round grilling! King-size Master bedroom suite with lavish Spa Bathroom complete with double vanity, glass steam shower & giant custom closet! Enjoy its private meditation deck! Large 2nd Bedroom, flexible 3rd Bedroom with custom built-ins for use as a media/guest room! Gleaming Hardwood floors! Extra deeded storage. (3rd Garage Space avail) Stunning!
